<div class="container">
  <%= simple_form_for(@mark_quarterbreed) do |f| %>
  <%= f.error_notification %>

  <h2 class="text-center"> JCI MARK QUARTERBREED KIT ORDER SHEET </h2>
  <p> Please complete as much information as you can - there are thousands of variations of my Jaguar kits. Phone numbers and Vehicle Identification Number (VIN) (serial number) are essential. Incomplete or <em> unsigned </em> forms will delay your order! We require payment in advance by <b> Cashier's Check or Money Order </b> in U.S. currency. <b> NO COD's</b>, personal checks, company checks, credit cards or wire transferes. <b> KITS ARE NOT RETURNABLE.</b> </p>

  <div class="panel panel-default col-xs-6">
  <h2 class="text-center">Mark Information (Before QB)</h2>
   <div class="row">
       <div class="col-xs-4">
         <h4>Model</h4>
         <%= f.input :mark_quarterbreeds_before_type, label: false, placeholder:"Type", collection: ["Mark 1", "Mark 2", "Mark VII", " Mark VIII", "Mark IX", "3.8 Sedan", "3.8S"]%>
       </div>
       <div class="col-xs-4">
         <h4>Year </h4>
         <%= f.input :mark_quarterbreeds_before_year, label: false, placeholder:"Year",  collection: ["1955", "1956", "1957", "1958", "1959", "1960", "1961", "1962", "1963", "1964", "1965", "1966", "1967"]%>
       </div>
       <div class="col-xs-4">
         <h4>VIN/ Body Number</h4>
         <%=f.input :mark_quarterbreeds_before_vin , label: false,  placeholder:"Vin #" %>
      </div>
   </div row>
   <div class"row">
     <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
       <p> VIN/ Body Number: Plate in the engine bay, Right Hand Block by oil filter </p>
     </div>
   </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-6">
          <h4>Trans </h4>
          <%= f.input :mark_quarterbreeds_before_trans, label: false, placeholder: "Trans", collection: ["Automatic", "Manuel"]%>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-6">
            <h4>Automatic Shifter </h4>
            <%= f.input :auto_shifter, label: false, placeholder: "Trans", collection: ["Column", "Dashboard"]%>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12">
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-4">
           <h4>Tire Size/Radius</h4>
           <%= f.input :mark_quarterbreeds_before_tire_size, label: false, placeholder: ""%>
       </div>
       <div class="col-xs-4">
            <h4>Rear Axle Ratio </h4>
            <%= f.input :mark_quarterbreeds_before_rear_axle_ratio, label: false, placeholder: "", collection: ["3.31", "3.54", "3.77", "4.07", "4.27", "Other - fill out in next box"]%>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-4">
          <h4>Other Axle Ratio </h4>
          <%= f.input :rear_axle_ratio_other, label: false, placeholder: ""%>
        </div>
       </div row>
       <div class="col-xs-12">
         <p> Rear Axle Ratio: Tag under bolt on rear cover, sometimes shown as a ratio (49/17) - just enter it in. </p>
       </div>

       <div class ="row">
         <div class="col-xs-8">
           <h4> Does the car have angle drive like pictured to the right?</h4>
           <%= f.collection_radio_buttons :angle_drive, [[true, 'Yes'], [false, 'No']], :first, :last%>
         </div>
         <div class="col-xs-4">
              <%= image_tag("angle_drive.png") %>
         </div>
         <div class="col-xs-12">
           <p> Note: If your Mark does not have this angle drive, order new angle drive and cable with kit. </p>
         </div>
       </div>
       <div class="row">
         <div class="col-xs-4">
              <h4>Speedo Number </h4>
              <%= f.input :mark_quarterbreeds_before_speedo, label: false, placeholder: "", collection: ["1080", "1100", "1152", "Other - fill out in next box"]%>
          </div>
         <div class="col-xs-4">
            <h4>Other Speedo </h4>
            <%= f.input :speedo_other, label: false, placeholder: ""%>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-4">
            <%= image_tag("speedo2.png") %>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="col-xs-12">
           <p class="p-form">Speedo Number: I need the 3 or 4 numbers in fine print near the center of the speedometer. See the arrow.</p>
         </div>

         <div class="row">
           <div class="col-xs-4">
               <h4>Installing or has a later model 4.2 motor with fuel injection? </h4>
               <%= f.collection_radio_buttons :motor_fuel_injection, [[true, 'Yes'], [false, 'No']], :first, :last %>
           </div>
            <div class="col-xs-4">
                <h4>XJ Engine Number </h4>
                <%= f.input :mark_quarterbreeds_before_engine_number, label: false, placeholder:"Engine Number"
                %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-4">
                <h4>Metal </h4>
                <%= f.input :xj_engine_number, label: false, placeholder:"", collection: ["Oil Pan", "Alloy", "Steel"]  %>
            </div>

          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
                  Engine Number is on the engline bellhousing flange, driver's side.
            </div>
          </div row>
 </div><!--panel-->

 <div class="panel panel-default col-xs-6">
   <h2 class="text-center">GM Trans Information</h2>
   <div class="row">
     <div class="col-xs-4">
       <h4> Trans: 700 </h4>
     </div>
